snippet.textDisplay: The rap in this melody (different than traditional hiphop beats) was new to me and I enjoyed the modern and young vocals of Prabhdeep and Rashmeet. The music had a chill vibe and was based on traditional sound and verses from Bullleh Shah. While some may find the sound unfamiliar and displeasing, this is exactly what Coke Studio aims to achieve, to deliver new and unfamiliar sounds. I am loving this season of Coke Studio India where they are bringing so many of these new non-mainstream artists who need visibility.
